{"id":108240,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/09/钓鱼岛，中华民族的泪珠/","date":"2010-09-27T03:29:36Z","modified":"2010-09-27T04:32:26Z","title":"钓鱼岛，中华民族的泪珠","content":"<p><p align=\"left\"><span>最近，中日间钓鱼岛之争有所升级。<span lang=\"EN-US\">2010</span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span>日一艘中国渔船与两艘日本巡逻艇在钓鱼岛海岸前发生碰撞，中国船员被日方扣押拘捕；之后中国船员被释放，但是船长仍被日方扣留。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span>日</span><span>因钓鱼岛撞船事件被抓的詹其雄船长，至今还被日本政府关押着。近百年来，因缺淡水而无人定居的钓鱼岛主权问题，一直是大陆、台湾和日本民众关注的焦点。</span></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><span>中国钓鱼岛在日本被称为尖阁诸岛，因为丰富的渔业资源以及石油与天然气资源而受到青睐。日本、中国和台湾都声称对这一组无人居住的岛屿享有主权。双方都从历史中寻找主权依据。但从历史角度看，钓鱼岛的领土归属问题并不那么明确。</span></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><span>中日之间的钓鱼岛主权争端起始于一百多年前。<span lang=\"EN-US\">1895</span>年，当时的中国清朝 ……</p>\n<p>……</span></p>\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\"><span></p>\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n</p>\n<p></span></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span><span><span></p>\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\"><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span><span></p>\n<p></span></span></span></span></span></span><strong><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span><span><span></p>\n<p><span></p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n<p></span></p>\n<p></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong></p>\n</p>\n<p></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p></p>\n","author":176,"categories":[1],"tags":[14